author: mkilwein
title: Freeform Star Tahj Mowry Had a Wild Time at Disney’s Animal Kingdom
text:
This past weekend, Tahj Mowry from Freeform’s “ Baby Daddy ” visited Disney’s Animal Kingdom and he was kind enough to share some of his pics with the Disney Parks Blog .
Tahj’s showed us how strong his selfie game was in front of the majestic Tree of Life. 

And he knew no visit is complete without concurring Expedition Everest – Legend of the Forbidden Mountain . 

Tahj also got to check out the “ Festival of the Lion King ” performance and even got a picture with the cast. We’re so jealous!
To catch more of Tahj, be sure to watch “Baby Daddy” on Mondays at 8:30/7:30c on Freeform.
